{"id": "1419745932584554660", "channel_id": "1419745932584554660", "type": 0, "author_id": "330608331251253248", "author_name": "neranz", "author_bot": false, "content": "I am a bit new to the game, and I don't have a lot of Caro awakeners, just Helot and Aigis. Ive played around with slotting in Chaos, but 24 doesn't seem to scale well with Pickman as a support (no str gen). Really struggling to see where he can fit in, despite liking his setup.\n\nI have access to Lily, Nautila, 24, Pandia, Karen, Hamlyn. And the story Awakeners.", "timestamp": "2025-09-22T18:03:27.932000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1419745932584554660", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Unsure what comp to run Pickman in.", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
